        <li>Flooring installation and replacement throughout</li>
        <li>Commercial renovation for Paia businesses — buildouts, reconfigurations, and facade improvements</li>
        <li>Custom metal fabrication — coastal-rated gates, railings, and fencing for North Shore properties</li>
        <li>Maui County permit management for all project types</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Getting to Paia — We Come to You</h2>
      <p>Paia is about 20 minutes from Central Maui and well within our regular service area. We visit properties throughout Paia, Haiku, Spreckelsville, Huelo, and the surrounding communities for free on-site estimates. There's no travel charge for North Shore projects — it's part of Maui, and Maui is our service area.</p>

      <p>Call (808) 795-4044 or request an estimate online. We'll schedule a visit, walk the project with you, and give you a clear, written estimate at no charge and no obligation.</p>

      <h2>Why Paia Property Owners Work With Us</h2>
      <p>Paia is a community that values authenticity, craftsmanship, and doing things the right way. That matches how we work. We're not a volume contractor running multiple large crews across dozens of simultaneous projects. We take on a focused volume of work, Noel stays personally involved, and the quality of execution reflects that engagement. For homeowners and business owners in Paia who want a contractor that operates with integrity and delivers quality work — that's what Great General LLC does.</p>
